{"tid":2323141,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"承諾舉行威爾斯獨立公投  繼蘇格蘭後  英國另一地方政黨倡議脫英獨立","createTime":"2020-12-13T02:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T00:40:31.000Z","uid":305299,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3f9d61dea176f9ac78e650d2979687eb4b7061","tid":2323141,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T02:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/igfbY94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FigfbY94.jpg&h=0d76782a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前，英國威爾斯地方政黨「威爾斯黨 (Plaid Cymru)」黨領袖彭偉思 (Adam Price) 公開承諾，如果明年勝出地方議會選舉執政，將會喺第一個任期之內舉行獨立公投。<br />\n<br />\n威爾斯黨係繼蘇格蘭民族黨 (SNP) 之後，另一地方政黨倡議表示明年地方選舉後爭取獨立，並將獨立議題帶入選戰之中。<br />\n<br />\n但有分析認為，威爾斯黨勝出地方議會選舉嘅機會並唔大。依家，威爾斯黨喺地方議會嘅60席入面，只有10席，而國會下議院650席入面，有40席係畫分畀威爾斯地區，但威爾斯黨亦只佔其中3席，影響力暫時有限。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>英國各地近年獨立呼聲四起</ins><br />\n由於英國係由四個構成國組成，分別係英格蘭、蘇格蘭、威爾斯及北愛爾蘭，假如明年威爾斯黨同蘇格蘭民族黨均勝出地方議會選舉，英國有可能喺5年內被分拆成四份。再加上基於《貝爾法斯特協議》嘅條文，北愛爾蘭可以隨時喺當地民意允許嘅情況下舉行公投，脫離英國同南面愛爾蘭共和國合併，所以英國最終只剩低英格蘭同海外領地亦恐怕唔再係小說入面嘅情節。<br />\n<br />\n但係，法理上，蘇格蘭同威爾斯進行獨立公投前，需要先獲得國會同意。除非蘇格蘭同威爾斯喺冇國會同意下私自舉行公投，否則成功舉行獨立公投嘅機會唔大。<br />\n<br />\n近年，英國各地嘅獨立呼聲抬頭，而且越來越受到重視，係同英國嘅脫歐爭議有緊密關係。脫歐過渡期將於本月底結束，而英國同歐盟仍未達成脫歐後協議，假如最後係冇協議下脫歐，屆時引發嘅經濟波動，有可能令英國各地嘅獨立呼聲有增冇減。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Plaid_Cymru/status/1337336034368040960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPlaid_Cymru%2Fstatus%2F1337336034368040960&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=c3e270f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPlaid_Cymru%2Fstatus%2F1337336034368040960&h=15348d1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Plaid_Cymru/status/1337336034368040960</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/politics/welsh-independence-price-senedd-referendum-19438732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walesonline.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fwelsh-independence-price-senedd-referendum-19438732&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=6b46d5c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/politics/welsh-independence-price-senedd-referendum-19438732</a>"},{"pid":"ae2169adf39f51fb0c2874e5097f2be754c10801","tid":2323141,"uid":61660,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"咁威爾斯親王係咪唔再存在"},{"pid":"aca1f49dfe4ec91cd2a4911c3e9effef64751f78","tid":2323141,"uid":5502,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"ae2169adf39f51fb0c2874e5097f2be754c10801","tid":2323141,"uid":61660,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"咁威爾斯親王係咪唔再存在"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:03:13.000Z","msg":"查理斯想做國王，去建立威爾斯王國可能仲快"},{"pid":"6de537060863903d69a9b99ebfc048d173bf2939","tid":2323141,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:07:51.000Z","msg":"係真係關脫歐事咩？即係想獨立後加入返歐盟？有冇民調顯示架，啲報道唔好帶風向喎"},{"pid":"f2c908e09b5e53698710c6abe075ec3292d53736","tid":2323141,"uid":143305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"鬼選到咩"},{"pid":"9089bc576e899ea9cb288f16f20a8d7bfd769f22","tid":2323141,"uid":26424,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T04:24:44.000Z","msg":"收中共俄羅斯錢分裂聯合王國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6c70f5848c0a7ff8d5e4241b840a3040448262","tid":2323141,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T04:27:42.000Z","msg":"唔覺威爾斯想獨立喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e42f48ebef33c48b56ce72bf2b92f56d53bfea","tid":2323141,"uid":32204,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6de537060863903d69a9b99ebfc048d173bf2939","tid":2323141,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:07:51.000Z","msg":"係真係關脫歐事咩？即係想獨立後加入